## Full Picture — How Data Flows

```
Each node (OS level)
    node-exporter running on master, node1, node2
        │ CPU, memory, disk, network stats
        ▼
Kubernetes API
    kube-state-metrics watching deployments, pods, services
        │ replica counts, pod phases, resource requests
        ▼
Prometheus
    scrapes both every 30 seconds, stores time-series data
        │
        ▼
Grafana
    queries Prometheus, draws charts you can actually read
        │
        ▼
You, in a browser, understanding what the cluster is doing
```
